== Media Player ==
The [http://www.videolan.org/vlc/ VLC Media Player] ([https://packages.debian.org/{{Stable_Whonix_based_on_Debian_codename}}/vlc Debian package]) is pre-installed in Whonix. Users do not face increased fingerprinting risks because [https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1369309 VLC does not run Javascript]. <ref>However, unrestricted access to the large number of codecs, along with the gstreamer and ffmpeg frameworks can expose the system to remote attacks. The risk is greater than with Tor Browser because the latter attempts to restrict codecs to a particular subset. [https://www.videolan.org/vlc/privacy.html No cookies are stored by VLC and no information is collected and sent.] [https://forums.whonix.org/t/vlc-fingerprinting-research/4897/6 Original thread]</ref>

<code>Start menu</code> -> <code>Multimedia</code> -> <code>VLC Media Player</code>

